---
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
---

<section class="mt-20" id="discipline">
  <div class="bento-card p-6 relative">
    <!-- Background Decoration -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.02]"
      style="background-image: linear-gradient(#fff 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #fff 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 50px 50px;"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row md:gap-14 gap-8 items-start relative z-10">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <Icon name="precision_manufacturing" size={24} class="text-primary" />
          <h2
            class="text-xl font-bold tracking-wide-soft text-white"
          >
            The Product Mindset
          </h2>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight-soft">
          Engineering for what matters.
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 pl-0 lg:pl-12 pt-4 lg:pt-0">
        <p class=" text-md font-normal text-text-soft leading-relaxed-soft tracking-normal-soft">
          I see code as a way to bring ideas to life, not just a way to fill repositories. My focus is on velocity without compromise: I use AI to handle the repetitive heavy lifting, which leaves me more room to think about your users, the architecture, and the actual value we are shipping. Whether itâ€™s an MVP or a complex system, my goal is to deliver excellence without the unnecessary noise.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
